            <div type="transcript" id="P91-43">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Remorse is memory awake,</l>
                    <l>Her companies astir, </l>
                    <l>A presence of departed acts</l>
                    <l>At window and at door.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It's past set down before the soul,</l>
                    <l>And lighted with a match,</l>
                    <l>Perusal to facilitate</l>
                    <l>Of its condensed despatch.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Remorse is cureless,  the disease</l>
                    <l>Not even God can heal;</l>
                    <l>For 't is his institution, </l>
                    <l>The complement of hell.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
